WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:18.000
When you look back over the long arc of your work, what question still feels most alive?

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:46.000
The question is always how a person comes into relation with what is unconscious, without being swallowed by it.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:01:14.000
So the task is not simply to remove symptoms, but to understand what they are expressing?

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:52.000
Yes. A symptom can be a messenger. The difficulty is to listen carefully enough and not rush too quickly to correction.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:02:25.000
In clinical work, how would you recognize that someone is ready for that kind of listening?

00:02:25.000 --> 00:03:08.000
One looks for stability, curiosity, and enough support in ordinary life. Without that, insight may become too heavy.
